{{Quote|If I were still in CorSec, I'd be calling for backup before setting foot in a place like this.|[[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]]|<ref name="X-Wing: Rogue Squadron">''[[X-Wing: Rogue Squadron]]''</ref>}}
'''DownTime''' was a [[Tapcafe/Legends|tapcafe]] located within the premises of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance's]] base on [[Folor]]. A smooth-rock cave, it had little illumination besides flashing neon light, and it stunk of sweat and liquor.

